te&utm_campaign=avatar_name)[Scilit](https://scilit.com/scholars?q=Waad%20Alhoshan)[Preprints.org](https://www.preprints.org/search?condition_blocks=[{%22value%22:%22Waad+Alhoshan%22,%22type%22:%22author%22,%22operator%22:null}]&sort_field=relevance&sort_dir=desc&page=1&exact_match=true)[Google Scholar](https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Waad+Alhoshan)\n\n *[](mailto:wmaboud@imamu.edu.sa)[![Image 8: ORCID](https://pub.mdpi-res.com/img/design/orcid.png?0465bc3812adeb52?1782113190)](https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3433-4653)\n\nComputer Science Department, College of Computer and Information Sciences, Imam Mohammad Ibn Saud Islamic University (IMSIU), Riyadh 11432, Saudi Arabia\n\n*\n\nAuthor to whom correspondence should be addressed. \n\n_Healthcare_**2026**, _14_(10), 1333; [https://doi.org/10.3390/healthcare14101333](https://doi.org/10.3390/healthcare14101333)\n\nSubmission received: 3 April 2026 / Revised: 2 May 2026 / Accepted: 8 May 2026 / Published: 13 May 2026\n\n (This article belongs to the Section [Artificial Intelligence in Healthcare](https://www.mdpi.com/journal/healthcare/sections/Artificial_Intelligence_in_Healthcare))\n\n[Download _keyboard\\_arrow\\_down_](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333)\n\n[Download PDF](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333/pdf?version=1778678794)\n\n[Download PDF with Cover](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333#)\n\n[Download XML](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333#)\n\n[Download Epub](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333/epub)\n\n[Browse Figures](https://www.mdpi.com/2227-9032/14/10/1333#)\n\n[](https://pub.mdpi-res.com/healthcare/healthcare-14-01333/article_deploy/html/images/healthcare-14-01333-g001.png?1778678888 \"\n                        <strong>Figure 1</strong><br/>\n                                                    <p>Schematic of a typical ASR–LLM clinical pipeline.</p>\n                                                \")[](https://pub.mdpi-res.com/healthcare/healthcare-14-01333/article_